 summarization methods\nwere measured using Latent Semantic Analysis (LSA) and Recall-Oriented\nUnderstudy for Gisting Evaluation (ROUGE) metrics to evaluate the reliability\nand validity of the model.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 23 Jul 2022 11:04:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 1 Aug 2022 14:33:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 2 Aug 2022 09:07:37 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 17 Nov 2022 16:44:34 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Fri, 18 Nov 2022 16:55:54 GMT"},{"version":"v6","created":"Mon, 28 Nov 2022 13:17:37 GMT"},{"version":"v7","created":"Tue, 30 May 2023 01:13:18 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-31"}
